ADS sum ReadEx command (ADSIGRP_SUMUP_READEX, 0xF083, 61571)
AdsRW  IOffs list size 
W: {list of IGrp, IOffs, Length} 
R: {list of results, Length} followed by {list of data (expepted lengths)}

